  <brief_title>Badalona Major Depressive Disorder Database Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Therapeutic Strategies for the Management of Patients With Major Depressive Disorder (MDD) and Suboptimal Response to Antidepressant Drugs in Primary Care: the Badalona Database Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
