  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A retrospective study using a data base of anonymized medical records. The purpose of the
      study is to examine the different therapeutic strategies for the management of patients with
      major depressive disorder (MDD) and suboptimal response to antidepressant drugs in primary
      care
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Therapeutic strategies for the management of patients with major depressive disorder (MDD)
      and suboptimal response to antidepressant drugs in primary care: the Badalona database study
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
